Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:58.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:04.27,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:10.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:17.78,sign_3220_4_The_Royal_Capita,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Capital of the Clover Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:28.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Time passed, and the title of Wizard King \Nhas been passed down to the present day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,where the Wizard King still \Nprotects this kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,along with his Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:40.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights have a total of \Nnine squads under the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:43.91,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They are squads of mages trained in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:51.26,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The band of heroes who risk their \Nlives to protect the kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Wizard King and the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:58.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,are what all citizens of the \NClover Kingdom aspire to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:16.84,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Path
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:34.04,sign_6476_37_Black_Bulls__Bas,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Black Bulls' Base
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:35.54,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand nine hundred and ninety-six...\NTwo thousand nine hundred and ninety-seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:40.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Two thousand nine hundred and ninety-eight...\NTwo thousand nine hundred and ninety-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Three thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to train... and train some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to get stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So I can become
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,the Wizard King before him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and go back for Sister Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:19.38,main,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought that even Asta \Nwould do so well as a Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.50,main,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it pays to live long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:27.77,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen years ago, Asta and Yuno were \Nabandoned in front of our church, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.09,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,How they've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.30,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the money they send us monthly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.78,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,we were able to fix our roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.77,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,and we won't be short on tatoes this winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:37.81,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.10,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.89,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.38,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.94,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.33,italics,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is everything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.41,italics,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.41,flashback,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,We've never had a Wizard King from this area,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:06.13,flashback,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,nor anyone who's actually achieved \Ngreatness in the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:10.86,flashback,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely hope that one of you \Nwill become the Wizard King someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.47,flashback,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.10,flashback,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:17.37,flashback,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,for the awarding... of the grimoires!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.28,flashback,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,This is my grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:37.37,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno received the legendary grimoire \Nwith the four-leaf clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.96,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.92,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However, Asta, who had no magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.59,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.97,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My grimoire's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:03.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now to down some moguro leaf juice \Nthat I haven't had in a while, since it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,supposedly increase magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.45,flashback,Guy A,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.89,flashback,Guy B,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.95,flashback,Guy C,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.83,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,What is that grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.25,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,That sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.55,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.13,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You little wretch with no magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:41.81,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,He... nullified my magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.02,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even without magical powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:51.72,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.28,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:08:01.54,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.86,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My very own grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:09.53,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how,\N but I was able to get one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.21,italics,Gandalf,0000,0000,0000,,Everything turned out all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:19.65,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, Asta... You're the \Npride of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.77,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.78,sign_12376_96_My_Observation_D,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(753,1)}My Observation Diary of My Very Best Friend, Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:44.29,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I encountered Asta was \Nat the Magic Knights Entrance Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:48.52,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,He shone from the moment I laid eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:05.23,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One of us is going to become the Wizard King.\NOur legend's beginning now, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:09.73,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show you just how much \NI've grown in six months...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.94,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.27,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are these birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:15.66,flashback,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:16.87,flashback,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.49,flashback,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty bad, even for \Nsomeone from the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.08,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me, you stupid birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.61,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:32.00,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the captains of \Nthe Magic Knights Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.77,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,All right. The next exam \Nshall be the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.39,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,You will engage in actual combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:47.60,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is our duty.\NShow us your true abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.36,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stand out by fighting \Nsomeone who looks strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.61,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Fight me, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:59.87,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sekke! You're willing to \Nfight a loser like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:08.00,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both give it our all and fight fair, \Nso we can achieve our goals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.04,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.41,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,No holding back, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.09,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Asta! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:24.10,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bronze Creation Magic: \NSekke Magnum Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.18,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to hold back.\NCome at me! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.47,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.03,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.05,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joining
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:52.00,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights so I can have a\Ngood time and avoid working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.67,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to work my butt off \Nand become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.68,sign_15775_127__So_cool__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"So cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.68,flashbackitalicstop,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.23,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,S-So much pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.05,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.24,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,the magical power of a \NMagic Knights Squad captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:25.12,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You said earlier that you wanted to \Nbecome the Wizard King, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.05,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm standing before you,\Ndo you still have the nerve
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.22,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,to say that you're going \Nto be the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.46,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,even without any magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:42.72,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even if I can't join the \NMagic Knights today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.68,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what anyone says to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:53.27,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going to become \Nthe Wizard King someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.70,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.66,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Join my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:12.83,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.04,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that I'll let \Nyou join the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.88,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the only one who had realized \NAsta's brilliance. The captain had, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:28.41,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Asta became a \Nmember of the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.69,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,And as for Asta's childhood friend, Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.48,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All who wish to offer, \Nplease raise your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.60,flashback,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.84,flashback,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.02,flashback,Synana,0000,0000,0000,,All of the captains...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.20,flashback,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,...raised their hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:45.35,flashback,Rooney,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:50.33,flashback,Tanoso,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought that only royalty and \Nnobles could join the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.83,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All of them! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:03.09,flashbackitalics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the best path to \Nbecoming the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.34,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to join the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.45,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Being Asta's childhood friend
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.29,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,would also make him Asta's \Nbest friend's childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.83,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,That would mean Yuno \Nand I are also best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:24.11,sign_19209_158_My_Observation_D,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(692,1)}My Observation Diary of My Very Best Friend's Best Friend, Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.61,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.85,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll write my entry for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:36.41,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,My dearest friend Asta was \Nworking hard again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.05,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Scrubbing the floors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.78,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:47.22,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Doing laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:14:00.44,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,B-But my heart belongs to Sister Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.69,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.69,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of the beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.20,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:18.65,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.58,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.52,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.01,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.29,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:36.74,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of heat is nothing to \Na member of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.41,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're getting out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:43.09,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not yet! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.24,flashback,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot. I want to add cold water. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:48.74,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging out naked really is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, he's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's been like that ever \Nsince our first mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,When we had to hunt that wild boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:25.15,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And when we finally got to Saussy Village, \Nwe ended up running into those weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.28,flashback,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.76,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.09,flashback,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,This is your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:03.14,flashback,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can \Nprotect those beasts now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.15,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.25,flashback,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:22.04,flashback,Heath,0000,0000,0000,,You have no chance of winning. \NWhy won't you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:26.04,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I give up, who's going to protect them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.95,flashback,ASta,0000,0000,0000,,I've realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:33.67,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just because of our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:36.29,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:38.39,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,so I can protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King, my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:46.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What does he think would've \Nhappened to him if I wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:50.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, I guess there have \Nbeen times where I thought he
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,may have actually done a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no! That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I care about that \Nshrimpy little peasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the dungeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.03,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.96,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.51,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.60,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.65,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Stupidsta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.57,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.03,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:37.07,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,defeat that guy, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.92,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw enough at him from the both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:53.30,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Move. I'm going to make that girl, \Nthat weakling, disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.40,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'll let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.56,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.22,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.67,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.86,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.12,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.63,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.21,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, at least he was okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.93,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:47.93,flashback,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.59,flashback,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Asta. I feel so much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.74,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Sorry for ruining the mixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.34,flashback,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:14.84,flashback,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta... D-Do you have \Nanyone that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.67,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! There's somebody \NI've got my heart set on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:26.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got your heart set on me,\Ndon't make me worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-S-S-Stupidsta! How long \Nhave you been standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I just got back from training!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:40.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.86,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's mission will be a bit rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.26,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Is your body back in tip-top shape, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.66,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,If your wounds still haven't healedâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.55,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:03.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:04.97,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:08.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing along someone who's\Nwounded would slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.39,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though I'm \Nactually worried about Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:12.98,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.34,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.46,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:21.47,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking it'd be nice \Nto ride on my broom tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.26,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.26,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take that much more \Nmagic to carry you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:32.54,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The thought of not wanting to be \Nseen on that ship by anyone I know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.74,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,never crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.81,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards! You dare mock my ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.46,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.46,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold it, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.57,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to act without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.42,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.22,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.23,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.98,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I need to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.41,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.34,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're poor, an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:08.07,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,or even us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:13.79,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can become greater than anyone \Nelse in this world. And to prove that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,To make Sister and everyone else happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:28.25,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can become the Wizard King!
