Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:06.09,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:10.74,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}It's Not as Though\NI'm Actually Worried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's Not as Though I'm Actually Worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:16.34,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's brushing each tooth carefully, \Nwith short strokes, ten to twenty times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:20.00,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't scrub so roughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:23.91,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The bubbles are heading toward his eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.93,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:30.76,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's not kicking off his blanket\Nand getting too cold, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:34.72,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind, it's almost creepy, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:36.49,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:41.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're off work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:44.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like all we ever do \Nlately is take time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:46.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to play with Rebecca's \Nyounger siblings, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:50.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 30: "The Mirror Mage."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:54.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 30\N\N{\fs18}The Mirror Mage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:53.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to play with all I've got!
